@startuml
'https://plantuml.com/sequence-diagram

title US15 - List Employees by Role (Sequence Diagram)

autoactivate on
autonumber

actor "Administrator" as ADM
participant ":ListEmployeesByRoleUI" as UI
participant ":ListEmployeesByRoleController" as Ctrl
participant ":StaffRepository" as Repo

activate ADM

ADM -> UI: Request list of employees by role
UI -> ADM: Ask for role/function
ADM --> UI: Enter role (e.g. "Nurse")

UI -> Ctrl: listEmployeesByRole(role)
Ctrl -> Repo: findByRole(role)
Repo --> Ctrl: list<StaffMember>
Ctrl --> UI: list<StaffMember>
UI --> ADM: Show employees for selected role

@enduml
